data.description: Don't miss out on this 4 bedroom (4th bedroom is bonus room w/closet) 2 bath home in Hendrix Farms sitting on almost a half acre lot (0.45). Exterior of the home features a new roof installed Nov 2023, privacy fence in rear(no back section), 2 patios, one from the living room and the other from primary bedroom.  Interior boasts an open concept with laminate flooring through living room, dining room, and kitchen.  Kitchen has stainless steel appliances and breakfast area. Primary bedroom has a spacious walk in closet, tray ceiling, and doors to patio area in backyard.  Primary bathroom features double vanity, separate tub and shower.  HVAC unit replaced Feb 2022.  Seller is willing to pay $6,000 in buyer concessions with acceptable offer.
